{"snp5.16:0.1":"Sutta Nipata 5.16 ","snp5.16:0.2":"Mogharajamanavapuccha ","snp5.16:1.1":"“Dvaham sakkam apucchissam, ","snp5.16:1.2":"(iccayasma mogharaja) ","snp5.16:1.3":"Na me byakasi cakkhuma; ","snp5.16:1.4":"Yavatatiyanca devisi, ","snp5.16:1.5":"Byakarotiti me sutam. ","snp5.16:2.1":"Ayam loko paro loko, ","snp5.16:2.2":"brahmaloko sadevako; ","snp5.16:2.3":"Ditthim te nabhijanati, ","snp5.16:2.4":"gotamassa yasassino. ","snp5.16:3.1":"Evam abhikkantadassavim, ","snp5.16:3.2":"atthi panhena agamam; ","snp5.16:3.3":"Katham lokam avekkhantam, ","snp5.16:3.4":"maccuraja na passati”. ","snp5.16:4.1":"“Sunnato lokam avekkhassu, ","snp5.16:4.2":"Mogharaja sada sato; ","snp5.16:4.3":"Attanuditthim uhacca, ","snp5.16:4.4":"Evam maccutaro siya; ","snp5.16:4.5":"Evam lokam avekkhantam, ","snp5.16:4.6":"Maccuraja na passati”ti. ","snp5.16:4.7":"Mogharajamanavapuccha pannarasama. "}